          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众神同走圆场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众神 （同喜迁莺） 只羡他功深德浩，只羡他功深德浩，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "因此上赐福天曹逍也么遥。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恁看那福自天来，将官品超。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这的是福禄自造，恁看他寿算弥高，恁看他寿算弥高。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众神",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "已到福地。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南极老人、牛郎、织女、张仙、财神",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请天官登台。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。天官上高台。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "天官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "天官",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "簇簇花香迎画阁，青青瑞草满阶庭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "天官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然好福地也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "南极老人、牛郎、织女、张仙、财神",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请天官赐福。"
        },
        {
          "character": "天官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小圣奉玉帝敕旨，进爵一品，愿位列朝班，公侯世代。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南极老人、牛郎、织女、张仙、财神",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天官赐福，正当如此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "天官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "诸位福神，各将福禄赐之。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南极老人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老人无以为赠，进献百寿图一轴，愿福寿绵长，筹添海屋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "牛郎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小仙敬献年年如意，岁岁平安，愿稻生双穗，五谷丰登。"
        },
        {
          "character": "织女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "织女敬献天丝文锦一缎，愿蚕桑茂盛，丝帛丰盈。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小仙特送麒麟为嗣，愿子孙繁衍，瓜瓞绵绵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "财神",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺财神特献黄金万两，愿财源茂盛，积玉堆金。"
        },
        {
          "character": "天官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众神 （同刮地风） 哎呀，万千春，享富贵，乐滔滔，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "庆长春，酒泛香醪。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "织女献丝帛绫绡。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "福寿弥高，盈仓廪，稷米豆丰满仓廒。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "佐皇家永享官爵。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乐善事，福禄根苗。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又只见半空中魁星献的祥云来罩。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（魁星上，跳舞，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "天官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "魁星献瑞，万代全福也。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众神 （同水仙子） 呀呀呀呀福分高，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀呀呀福分高。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "羡羡羡，羡文才锦绣好。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贺贺贺，贺百福骈臻妙。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "道道道，道民乐欢天乐。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺俺俺，俺将这喜事儿留与后人标。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。天官下高台，坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "南极老人、牛郎、织女、张仙、财神",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赐福已全。"
        },
        {
          "character": "天官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一同覆奏上帝去者。"
        },
        {
          "character": "南极老人、牛郎、织女、张仙、财神",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众神 （同煞尾） 列旌幢一派仙音绕，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只愿普天下积德的享福禄直到老。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。众神同下。）"
        }
      ],
